frames.caption: A large scorpion crawls across the sandy desert under the moonlit sky. The moon casts a soft glow, highlighting the scorpion's detailed exoskeleton. The scene is set against a backdrop of distant dunes and a clear night sky.
frames.description: The scene captures a nocturnal desert environment with a focus on a scorpion navigating the sandy terrain. The moon provides a serene and mysterious atmosphere, enhancing the natural beauty of the desert landscape.

frames.caption: A large, detailed insect stands prominently in a desert landscape under a bright full moon. The creature's segmented body and pincers are highlighted against the dark night sky, creating a dramatic and surreal scene.
frames.description: The scene depicts a close-up of a large insect, possibly a scorpion or similar arthropod, in a desert setting at night. The full moon illuminates the sandy terrain, casting shadows and highlighting the intricate details of the creature's exoskeleton.
